### Get all images. Each request **MUST** be delimited by a triple hash

# This is a comment

GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InRlc3R1c2VyX25ld0BleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsImlhdCI6MTc3NDA3MzY5NiwiZXhwIjoxNzc0MTYwMDk2fQ.NCU55_2cAwwm_bv_WIzMRarMwMuvmMAR5eHU9rjk6SA


### A second example. Each request **MUST** be delimited by a triple hash

POST http://localhost:3000/api/test HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json # Content-Type header is a must if you're sending JSON

{
  "a": 1,
  "b": 2
}


