### Create User

# [Account Creation] 201 Created — new unique user
# Expect: 201 Created + auth token in body

POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser_new@example.com",
  "name": "testuser_new",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "714-376-9559",
  "type": "agent"
}


### Create User

